    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To add clear button on mui textfield, set this   event of the mui textfield. It will clear the mui textfield. Today, I‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To add clear button on mui textfield, set this <code class=\"language-text\">setValue</code> <code class=\"language-text\">onClick</code> event of the mui textfield. It will clear the mui textfield.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add clear button on mui textfield in react js.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui textfield in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material textfield clear button example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of making clear button input using mui textfield.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Box <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/Box'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> InputAdornment <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/InputAdornment'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> TextField <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/TextField'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Button <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/Button'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">ClearTextField</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Original Val\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Box m<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>TextField\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">newValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token function\">setValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>newValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        variant<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"outlined\"</span>\n        defaultValue<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"TextField\"</span>\n        InputProps<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token literal-property property\">endAdornment</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>InputAdornment position<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"end\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n              <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Button\n                variant<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"outlined\"</span>\n                onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                  <span class=\"token function\">setValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n              <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n                Clear button\n              <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n            <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>InputAdornment<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Box<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> TextField component and added clear button of MUI Textfield.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/d6bfc/clear-button.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.56962025316456%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, Mui Textfield Clear Button\"\n        title=\"React, Mui Textfield Clear Button\"\n        src=\"/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/828fb/clear-button.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/ff44c/clear-button.jpg 158w,\n/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/a6688/clear-button.jpg 315w,\n/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/828fb/clear-button.jpg 630w,\n/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/0ede0/clear-button.jpg 945w,\n/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/3ac88/clear-button.jpg 1260w,\n/static/ca1499bb73a5618cd5519f043239dd6c/d6bfc/clear-button.jpg 1363w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add clear button on mui textfield in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"November 15, 2022","description":"Example of add clear button on mui textfield in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to make time input using mui textfield in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-16-how-to-make-time-input-using-mui-textfield-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add icon in right side on mui textfield in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-15-how-to-add-icon-in-right-side-on-mui-textfield-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-15-how-to-add-clear-button-on-mui-textfield-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2022-11-16-how-to-make-time-input-using-mui-textfield-in-react-js/","nextSlug"